{
  "stem": "18397.3",
  "chunk_idx": 4,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 14.2,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "I had to bring in something, or to sell something.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "You can-- we-- the Germans didn't-- they were supposed to, maybe.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Maybe they paid something to the-- the ghetto government.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "But-- but you couldn't see it.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "You couldn't get paid.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "But it wasn't too much, the pay was nothing.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "The only money I needed when I came from the woods, I had to have a haircut.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "I didn't have it for a year.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So I had to pay the barber.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Well, you know--",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "[LAUGHTER]",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "When I got in the ghetto, they took me to the-- to the-- to the partisans because they needed me.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I was a specialist in all this-- all this garbage.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So I was in the activities.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And when I became an instructor to handle arms, you know, a rifle and these things, a lot of the-- the guys who got killed over there, were wounded, they didn't know-- and-- and bullets was a big deal.",
      "word_count": 39
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "You-- you could-- you could have an arms, but you could have two bullets.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "You couldn't buy no more.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "What's two bullets?",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "See, it was very bad.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Then I became-- I became involved with a guy, Ring, not the [INAUDIBLE].",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "[INAUDIBLE] Ring, he was a-- a-- refugee.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And he-- he really was a very talented guy.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "He-- and I know him before the ghetto.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And-- and-- and they ask for-- for policemen, you know, this-- they're working, the police.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So a lot of guys went there.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "If you had experience, you know, like a soldier or something.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Then I say, it's not for me.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "So I say, you stay and the police go [INAUDIBLE].",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "He became a-- a commissar, you know, one of the top.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And then was a guy, with an organization, it was politics.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "One-- one organization was communist.",
      "word_count": 5
    }
  ],
